== 战役进程 ==
=== 第一次战役 ===
;3月2日
反卡武装胜利。

;战力：
*反卡势力：300-350个士兵，一辆坦克，许多辆[[武裝改裝車|武裝改裝車]]；
*卡部队：200-400个士兵，两架攻击性战机，50辆武裝改裝車，120mm[[火炮|火炮]]；

;死伤：
*反卡势力：14死<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-12643311 Libya revolt: Rebels say no talks unless Gaddafi goes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-12643311 |date=20110316072919 }}. ''[[BBC_News|BBC News]]''. 2011-03-03.</ref>，12被俘<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/gaddafis-men-poised-to-strike-at-benghazi-2240487.html# |title=Gaddafi's men poised to strike at Benghazi - Africa, World |publisher=The Independent |date=1994-01-11 |accessdate=2011-03-13 |archive-date=2019-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130162315/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/gaddafis-men-poised-to-strike-at-benghazi-2240487.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，28伤<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/blogs-and-stories/2011-03-04/inside-libyas-rebel-movement/ |title=Inside Libya's Rebel Movement |publisher=The Daily Beast |date=2011-03-04 |accessdate=2011-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110309183917/http://www.thedailybeast.com/blogs-and-stories/2011-03-04/inside-libyas-rebel-movement/ |archive-date=2011-03-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>；
*卡部队：2-10死<ref name="au.news.yahoo.com">{{cite web |url=http://au.news.yahoo.com/world/a/-/world/8942525/gaddafi-stages-east-libya-offensive-rebels-defiant/ |title=Gaddafi stages east Libya offensive, rebels defiant - Yahoo!7 |publisher=Au.news.yahoo.com |date=2011-03-03 |accessdate=2011-03-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121209033506/http://au.news.yahoo.com/world/a/-/world/8942525/gaddafi-stages-east-libya-offensive-rebels-defiant/ |archivedate=2012-12-09 }}</ref>，4被俘，一架[[:en:Dassault_Mirage_F1|F1]]被击落；

